==============================================
Universal Interfaces & Libraries Release Notes 
==============================================

Version: Universal Interfaces 3.3.2
Date:    April 27, 2000
Author:  Nick Kledzik


=================
Important Notice
=================

This set of headers and libraries supports
CarbonLib 1.0.2 and QuickTime 4.1 development.

See 3.3 and 3.3.1 Release Notes for information on 
changes from 3.2 to 3.3.1.


==================================================
Changes since Universal Interfaces 3.3.1
==================================================

-  Fixes to .k.h files:
		AVComponents.k.h
		MediaHandlers.k.h
		Movies.k.h
		QTStreamingComponents.k.h
		QuickTimeComponents.k.h
		Sound.k.h

-  Fix whitespace in comments.  In 3.3.1 headers all tabs
   where stripped, but in some cases alignment was not preserved.

-  Fix URLAccess.h to use #define instead of const char* for strings

-  Fix InputSprocket.h to compile with carbon.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------
Nick Kledzik
Universal Interfaces 
Apple Computer, Inc.

